    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001082_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add place="marginleft" hand="#U" rend="left diagonal"><hi rend="blue"><metamark/><!-- circle -->18</hi></add><space extent="1" unit="words"/><placeName>Drumcondra Castle</placeName>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="words"/><date when="1857-08-22">28<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> August
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="words"/>1857</date></p>
<lb/>   
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear Brother</p>
<lb/><p>As there is
<lb/>some time between
<lb/>this and the publication
<lb/>I think we can wait
<lb/>and I shall consult
<lb/><persName>Murray</persName> as he
<lb/>intended the <placeName><geogName type="waterfall">Falls</geogName></placeName><!-- geog: Victoria Falls -->
<lb/>for the beginning of
<lb/>the Book.

	<pb facs="liv_001082_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>Please send me
<lb/>at once a sheet
<lb/>or two containing
<lb/>the explanation
<lb/>of the difference
<lb/>of amount of
<lb/>rain south &amp;
<lb/>North of the Equator
<lb/>the sheet contains
<lb/>a note by <persName>Babinet</persName>
<lb/>the <term type="person">Frenchman</term> - the
<lb/>other a note by

	<pb facs="liv_001082_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/><persName>Gabriel</persName> &amp; <persName>Brand</persName>
<lb/>I need them for
<lb/>my <choice><sic><date when="1857-08-31">Monday</date>s</sic><corr><date when="1857-08-31">Monday</date>'s</corr></choice> speech
<lb/>Will leave on
<lb/><date when="1857-08-31">Monday</date> night in
<lb/>order to be at
<lb/><choice><sic><persName>Captain <unclear>Trotter</unclear></persName>s</sic><corr><persName>Captain <unclear>Trotter</unclear></persName>'s</corr></choice>
<lb/>wrote <persName>Mary</persName> this
<lb/>morning. <space extent="1" unit="words"/>1400
<lb/>tickets of admission
<lb/>have been bought
<lb/>in <placeName><settlement type="city">Dublin</settlement></placeName>. The
<lb/><term type="tribe">Bechuana</term> reed
<lb/>dance may be

	<pb facs="liv_001082_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>put in where the
<lb/><term type="tribe">Makololo</term> dance is
<lb/>described - the
<lb/><term type="animal">Buffalo</term> is mentioned
<lb/>on the <placeName><geogName type="river">Leambye</geogName></placeName> <add place="above">near <placeName><settlement>Sesheke</settlement></placeName></add> &amp;
<lb/>again below
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="village"><persName>Mpende</persName>'s</settlement></placeName> or <placeName><settlement type="village"><app><rdg>Borowa</rdg><rdg>Boroma</rdg></app></settlement></placeName>
<lb/>if I succeed in getting
<lb/>to <choice><sic><persName>Captain <unclear>Trotter</unclear></persName>s</sic><corr><persName>Captain <unclear>Trotter</unclear></persName>'s</corr></choice>
<lb/>on <date when="1857-09-01"><choice><sic>tuesday</sic><corr>Tuesday</corr></choice></date> I would
<lb/>sleep at <choice><sic><persName>M<hi rend="sup">s</hi> Taylor</persName>'s</sic><corr><persName>M<hi rend="sup">s</hi> Taylor</persName>'s</corr></choice>
<lb/>&amp; then join you at
<lb/><persName>Helen</persName>'s on <date when="1857-09-02">Wednesday</date>.</p><!-- there is actually no visible closer, leaving as is. BL-->


            </div>
